					<a href="https://dev.to/maurerkrisztian" target="_blank"><span class="role">✏️ Writer <span class="invert">✏️ Writer</span></span></a>
				</div>
				<p class="desc">I'm a full stack web developer with some IoT, devops skills, & freelancer.</p>
			</div>
		</header>
		<main class="wrapper mt4 mb4">
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="section">
					<h3 class="sectionTitle">About me</h3>
					<p class="bio">
						<span>Hello! 👋</span>I'm Maurer Krisztián Programming it's a hobby for me I don't see just as a job. I'm fast learner and could learn autodidactically with good problem solving skills.
